"Override B<hwclock>\\(aqs default rtc device file name. Otherwise it will "
"use the first one found in this order: I</dev/rtc0>, I</dev/rtc>, I</dev/"
"misc/rtc>. For B<IA-64:> I</dev/efirtc> I</dev/misc/efirtc>"
msgstr ""

